  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b90.\u0ba8\u0bbe. \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Use of troops to disperse protesters worrisome - UN Council's Resident Representative for Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "United Nations Resident Representative for Sri Lanka Hana Singer Hamdi has said that the use of soldiers to disperse the protesters is worrying.",
        "Early this morning, the three forces removed the people who were peacefully protesting in front of the Presidential Secretariat located in Gallimugattidal area of \u200b\u200bColombo.",
        "In this case, United Nations Resident Representative for Sri Lanka Hana Singer Hamdi has expressed her concern on her Twitter page.",
        "The use of the army to disperse the protesters is worrisome. Journalists and human rights defenders have the right to monitor demonstrations. Therefore, the UN said that their activities should not be hindered. Hana Singer Hamdi, Resident Representative of the Council for Sri Lanka said."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "worrisome - UN Council's Resident Representative for Sri Lanka",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
